∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : ℂ → ℂ),
  IsHolomorphic f → IsLoop γ → (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : ℂ → ℂ)
  [inst_2 : IsClosed γ], Holomorphic f → ∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : ℂ → ℂ),
  HolomorphicOn ℂ f (Set.range γ) → IsClosed (Set.range γ) → (∮ z, f z ∂γ) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : Path ℂ),
  IsHolomorphicOn f (Set.range γ) → (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : Path ℂ),
  (∀ z, ComplexDifferentiableAt ℂ f z) → (∮ z in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : ℂ → ℂ), 
  IsClosedPath γ → HolomorphicOn f (Set.range γ) → (∮ z in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : ℂ → ℂ) (hγ : IsClosed γ),
  HolomorphicOn ℂ f (Set.range γ) → (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_2} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (γ : Path ℂ) (f : ℂ → E),
  IsHolomorphic f → ∮ z in γ, f z = 0

∀ {f : ℂ → ℂ} {γ : ℂ → ℂ} (holo_f : Differentiable ℂ f) (closed_γ : PathClosed γ),
  (∮ z in closed_γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : ℂ → ℂ)
  (hγ : Continuous γ) (hγ_closed : γ 0 = γ 1),
  (∀ z, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) → (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z) = 0
